<varlistentry>
<term><envar>MIKTEX_EDITOR</envar></term>
<listitem>
<indexterm>
<primary>MIKTEX_EDITOR</primary>
</indexterm>
<para>The editor to use when selecting <userinput>e</userinput> in the error prompt menu.</para>
<para>The value can contain these placesholder:</para>
<variablelist>
<varlistentry>
<term><option>%f</option></term>
<listitem><para>The name of the file, which contains the erroneous
line of &TeX; code.</para></listitem>
</varlistentry>
<varlistentry>
<term><option>%l</option></term>
<listitem><para>The line number.</para></listitem>
</varlistentry>
</variablelist>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>
